MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Beyond_the_reach_of_falcon_s_flight
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 129
  mythName: Beyond the reach of falcon' s flight
  omens:
  - '1. The silhouette of the Citadel appears on

    the horizon, teetering and
    crooked. Any

    Seers you meet warn you not to go there.'
  - '2. The nearest Seer skulks between the

    trees, seeking a new Sanctum so
    that the

    Watcher will not find them.'
  - '3. Iron hounds, forged in the Citadel, scour

    the land, terrorising but
    not harming

    Seers. A pack of four charge past the

    Company, heading
    to the nearest Seer.'
  - '4. The Watcher from the Citadel is seeking

    out every Seer, warning them
    not to

    interfere with the destiny of the Realm.'
  - '5. A glowing orb falls from the sky, landing

    with an explosion in the nearby
    woods.

    Screams follow from the crash site, and

    an Immolated Seer bursts
    from the

    woods. In their death throes they attack

    any nearby, losing
    d6 VIG each round.'
  - '6. The Citadel glows, flooding the Realm

    with intense white light. Seers
    scream.

    When the light fades the Citadel is gone.'
  verse: 'Omens

    1. The silhouette of the Citadel appears on

    the horizon,
    teetering and crooked. Any

    Seers you meet warn you not to go there.

    2.
    The nearest Seer skulks between the

    trees, seeking a new Sanctum so that
    the

    Watcher will not find them.

    3. Iron hounds, forged in the Citadel,
    scour

    the land, terrorising but not harming

    Seers. A pack of four charge
    past the

    Company, heading to the nearest Seer.

    4. The Watcher from
    the Citadel is seeking

    out every Seer, warning them not to

    interfere
    with the destiny of the Realm.

    5. A glowing orb falls from the sky, landing

    with
    an explosion in the nearby woods.

    Screams follow from the crash site, and

    an
    Immolated Seer bursts from the

    woods. In their death throes they attack

    any
    nearby, losing d6 VIG each round.

    6. The Citadel glows, flooding the Realm

    with
    intense white light. Seers scream.

    When the light fades the Citadel is gone.

    Cast

    The
    Watcher in the Citadel, Setizi

    VIG 12, CLA 17, SPI 15, 8 GD

    A1 (silver
    mail). Can Focus.

    Glassy longsword (2d8 hefty), crystal lantern

    (peering
    into it gives a hazy view of a

    location within the Realm that you have

    visited.
    Light causes pain to Seers)

    Protecting a destined future (see below).

    Immolated
    Seer

    VIG 10, CLA 7, SPI 7, 6 GD

    Bursts of anguished flames (d8 blast)

    Iron
    Hound

    VIG 10, CLA 12, SPI 2, 2 GD

    A3 (metallic body)

    Forged jaws
    (d8), focused on their quarry

    A watcher yond our earthly sight'
  castEntries:
  - name: The Watcher in the Citadel, Setizi
    statBlock: 'VIG 12, CLA 17, SPI 15, 8 GD

      A1 (silver mail). Can Focus.'
    notes: 'Glassy longsword (2d8 hefty), crystal lantern

      (peering into it
      gives a hazy view of a

      location within the Realm that you have

      visited.
      Light causes pain to Seers)

      Protecting a destined future (see below).'
  - name: Immolated Seer
    statBlock: 'VIG 10, CLA 7, SPI 7, 6 GD

      Bursts of anguished flames (d8
      blast)'
    notes: 
  - name: Iron Hound
    statBlock: 'VIG 10, CLA 12, SPI 2, 2 GD

      A3 (metallic body)'
    notes: 'Forged jaws (d8), focused on their quarry

      A watcher yond our earthly
      sight

      Beyond the reach of falcon'' s flight

      DESTINED FUTURE

      Subject
      Destiny

      1 Ruler of the Realm Must die next Season

      2 A Seer Must
      leave the Realm

      3 A member of the

      Company

      Must be imprisoned
      in

      the Citadel

      4 A Knight Must die

      5 A Vassal Must find
      the City

      6 A courtier Must rule the Realm

      Citadel

      Dwelling:
      Harpist gathering ~ Sanctum: Lullaby stream ~ Monument: Marble mesa

      Hazard:
      Draining dunes ~ Curse: Gorge of sorrow ~ Ruin: Broken tools

      Th'
  flavorTable:
    title: DESTINED FUTURE
    rows:
    - 1 Ruler of the Realm Must die next Season
    - 2 A Seer Must leave the Realm
    - '3 A member of the

      Company

      Must be imprisoned in

      the Citadel'
    - 4 A Knight Must die
    - 5 A Vassal Must find the City
    - '6 A courtier Must rule the Realm

      Citadel'
  dwelling: Harpist gathering
  sanctum: Lullaby stream
  monument: Marble mesa
  hazard: Draining dunes
  curse: Gorge of sorrow
  ruin: Broken tools
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
